OL,3,CLegacy police probe: Can anyone be a
OL,4,Cfuneral director?
OL,6,FA police investigation into a funerals
OL,7,Fbusiness in East Yorkshire has raised
OL,8,Fquestions about the regulation of the
OL,9,Findustry.
OL,11,FLegacy Independent Funeral Directors,
OL,12,Fbased in Hull, is at the centre of an
OL,13,Finquiry into the storage and care of
OL,14,Fbodies after on 6 March.
OL,16,FAfter the company's three premises
OL,17,Fwere cordoned off police removed 35
OL,18,Fbodies, as well as a quantity of ashes.
