OL,3,CLegacy police probe: Can anyone be a
OL,4,Cfuneral director?
OL,6,FTwo people have been arrested. More
OL,7,Fthan 1,000 calls have been made to a
OL,8,Fspecial hotline set up by
OL,9,Finvestigators.
OL,11,FWhat police have called a "horrific
OL,12,Fincident" has now led to calls for the
OL,13,Findustry to be more carefully
OL,14,Fscrutinised.
OL,16,FCan anyone become a funeral director?
OL,18,FEffectively, yes. There is no formal
OL,19,Froute into the industry and no
OL,20,Fmandatory qualifications.
