OL,6,FAccording to the government's website:
OL,7,F"You can get into this job by doing an
OL,8,Fapprenticeship or working your way up."
OL,10,FGCSEs, including English and maths,
OL,11,Fmay help and there are professional
OL,12,Fqualifications, including an NVQ in
OL,13,Ffuneral service and operations.
OL,15,FEntry level pay is around #19,000,
OL,16,Frising to #27,000 and beyond with
OL,17,Fexperience.
