OL,3,CLegacy police probe: Can anyone be a
OL,4,Cfuneral director?
OL,6,FNo. The investigation into Legacy
OL,7,FIndependent Funeral Directors has
OL,8,Fexposed what many people see as a flaw
OL,9,Fin maintaining standards the industry.
OL,11,FHull West and Hessle MP Emma Hardy
OL,12,Fsaid: "Many people were shocked when
OL,13,Fthe investigation started into the
OL,14,Ffuneral home that regulations don't
OL,15,Fexist. Nothing is statutory and
OL,16,Fnothing is compulsory.
