OL,6,F"I think this is a major gap in our
OL,7,Fsystem of regulation, I think it's
OL,8,Fsomething that is really important to
OL,9,Freassure the community and reassure
OL,10,Fpeople who are in the most vulnerable
OL,11,Fstages of bereavement.
OL,13,F"Of course the vast majority (of
OL,14,Ffuneral directors) are decent people
OL,15,Fdoing a good job but if we had that
OL,16,Fsystem of regulation it gives that
OL,17,Fpeace of mind."
