OL,3,CLegacy police probe: Can anyone be a
OL,4,Cfuneral director?
OL,6,FThere are two professional bodies for
OL,7,Fthe industry: the National Association
OL,8,Fof Funeral Directors and the National
OL,9,FSociety of Allied and Independent
OL,10,FFuneral Directors.
OL,12,FAccording to the NAFD, which has
OL,13,Fexisted for 120 years, its role is to
OL,14,Fprovide "advice, advocacy, education
OL,15,Fand support to help them meet the
OL,16,Fhighest professional standards".
