OL,3,CLegacy police probe: Can anyone be a
OL,4,Cfuneral director?
OL,6,FBut membership is entirely voluntary.
OL,7,FLegacy Independent Funeral Directors
OL,8,Fbecame a member in 2011 but the NAFD
OL,9,Fsaid the company gave up its
OL,10,Fmembership in 2021.
OL,12,FChief executive Andrew Judd said: "At
OL,13,Fthe moment, most people think that to
OL,14,Ftrade as a funeral director you have
OL,15,Fto be qualified, many think you have
OL,16,Fto be licensed and many think that
OL,17,Fthere is a statutory standard.
