OL,6,F"The reality is that there isn't and
OL,7,Fwe are campaigning to allow the trade
OL,8,Fassociations within the sector to have
OL,9,Fthe support of a statutory framework
OL,10,Fto ensure that the high standards and
OL,11,Foversight that our members currently
OL,12,Fundergo become commonplace.
OL,14,F"We want to make sure that people are
OL,15,Freassured that funeral directors
OL,16,Fcannot trade unless they subscribe to
OL,17,Fan agreed and level playing field in
OL,18,Fterms of standards and care."
