OL,3,CLegacy police probe: Can anyone be a
OL,4,Cfuneral director?
OL,6,FThe NAFD says bereaved families should
OL,7,Fdo their research, choosing businesses
OL,8,Fwhich are members of a credible trade
OL,9,Fassociation.
OL,11,FMr Judd said: "What we would encourage
OL,12,Fis visit your funeral director, meet
OL,13,Fthem, meet the team who are going to
OL,14,Fcaring for your loved one and, if you
OL,15,Fwant to and if you're interested, you
OL,16,Fshould ask to see their back-of-house
OL,17,Ffacilities, to see where your loved
OL,18,Fone will be stored and cared for."
